Center: Centre for Photonuclear Experiments Data, Moscow State University, Russia
title: Experimental investigation of the shell effects in giant resonance for the nucleus Al-27.

x4freetext: Experimental investigation of the shell effects in
giant resonance for the nucleus Al-27.

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Soviet Journal of Nuclear Physics, Vol.33, p.453 (1981)

x4freetext: Photoproton spectra from the nucleus Al-27 are obtained
at 14 values of the gamma-ray bremsstrahlung upper
boundary (Eg-max or En-max) in the energy interval
Eg-max=17.0-29.7 MeV. The partial cross sections of the
photoproton reaction are calculated for production of
the final nucleus in the ground state, in two lower
excited states and in the state groups with the
